# Mobile-First Responsive Design Standards

## Breakpoint System
- **xs:** 0-639px (mobile portrait)
- **sm:** 640px+ (mobile landscape) 
- **md:** 768px+ (tablet portrait)
- **lg:** 1024px+ (tablet landscape/small desktop)
- **xl:** 1280px+ (desktop)
- **2xl:** 1536px+ (large desktop)

## Mobile Navigation Standards

### AppHeader Mobile Layout
```vue
<!-- Mobile-first header structure -->
<header class="bg-surface border-b border-border sticky top-0 z-40">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <!-- Mobile: Stack vertically, Desktop: Horizontal -->
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between items-start sm:items-center h-auto sm:h-16 py-3 sm:py-0">
      
      <!-- Logo - Always visible -->
      <div class="flex items-center w-full sm:w-auto justify-between sm:justify-start">
        <router-link to="/dashboard" class="flex items-center">
          <div class="h-8 w-8 sm:h-10 sm:w-10 bg-action/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-2 sm:mr-3">
            <!-- Logo icon -->
          </div>
          <span class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-heading font-bold text-text">ECIS Portal</span>
        </router-link>
        
        <!-- Mobile menu toggle - Only on mobile -->
        <button class="sm:hidden p-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-surface-2">
          <!-- Hamburger icon -->
        </button>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Desktop Navigation - Hidden on mobile -->
      <nav class="hidden sm:flex items-center space-x-1">
        <!-- Navigation items -->
      </nav>
      
      <!-- Mobile Navigation - Full width on mobile -->
      <nav v-if="showMobileMenu" class="sm:hidden w-full mt-4 pt-4 border-t border-border">
        <!-- Mobile navigation items -->
      </nav>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>
```

