## Mobile Typography Scale

### Responsive Text Sizes
```css
/* Mobile-first typography */
.text-mobile-xs { @apply text-xs; }      /* 12px */
.text-mobile-sm { @apply text-sm; }     /* 14px */
.text-mobile-base { @apply text-base; } /* 16px */
.text-mobile-lg { @apply text-lg; }     /* 18px */
.text-mobile-xl { @apply text-xl; }     /* 20px */

/* Desktop scaling */
@media (min-width: 640px) {
  .text-mobile-xs { @apply text-sm; }      /* 14px */
  .text-mobile-sm { @apply text-base; }    /* 16px */
  .text-mobile-base { @apply text-lg; }    /* 18px */
  .text-mobile-lg { @apply text-xl; }      /* 20px */
  .text-mobile-xl { @apply text-2xl; }     /* 24px */
}
```

